Class CommandHandler

    org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor, org.bukkit.command.TabCompleter, org.bukkit.event.Listener

    public class CommandHandler
extends PluginHandler
implements org.bukkit.command.TabCompleter, org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor
    Convenience implementation of CommandExecutor and TabCompleter, for handling PluginCommands.
